    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "758 乾元元年 置浙江西道節度兼江寧軍使，領昇、潤、宣、歙、饒、江、蘇、常、杭、湖十州，治昇州，尋徙治蘇州，未幾，罷領宣、歙、饒三州，副使兼餘杭軍使，治杭州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "置浙江東道節度使，領越、睦、衢、婺、臺、明、處、溫八州，治越州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "改福建經略使為都防禦使兼寧海軍使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "置洪吉都防禦團練觀察處置使兼莫傜軍使，領洪、吉、虔、撫、袁五州，治洪州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "置宣歙饒觀察使，治宣州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "759 二年 劍南東川增領昌、渝、合三州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "沔州隸鄂岳節度，壽州隸淮西節度。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "廢浙江西道節度使，置觀察處置都團練守捉及本道營田使，更領丹陽軍使，治蘇州，復領宣、歙、饒三州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "廢宣歙饒觀察使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "置鄂、岳、沔三州都團練守捉使，治鄂州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
